description: I have a very nice Cabin cruiser for sale or possible trades considered. This boat has a shower toilet bathroom sink flat screen tv aft bedroom dinning table A/C microwave stove on board charging system and battery power for use without shore cord which is included it has everything even then  kitchen sink. The drivers seat is decent and the lounge seat but could use a upholstery job. The engine and outdrive  is a volvo penta original with low hours and runs perfect. I have spent a lot of money on this boat and maintenance has been done sincerely. Has a brand new 4 blade prop new hydraulic tilt trim cylinders and new pump. New fuel pump new fuel water separator filter new fish depth finder with gps has rod holders a bait tank bag attaches to the rear a nice teak wood rear deck also comes with  a dual axle $3500 aluminum trailer with surge brakes.  Also includes storage cover and a full enclosure for winter months call or text please. The South Carolina Gamecocks decals are removable if your not a fan but this boat gets a lot of attention and is a great way to enjoy the lake with family and friends staying overnight is like your own personal portable condo on the water. The only reason I am selling is I am trying to pay off all my bills so I can retire in a couple years and buy my condo at the beach. Trades are considered if its something I can sell quickly and get the money or something I want only. Don't miss the chance to get a nice boat at a 10th of the price of a new one.Regal is one of the top 5 boat manufactures and are very well made and hold value well this one will not go down in value only up. We can set up a test run on lake Wylie depending on the water level of course but boat is not junk and runs well.
title: 1989 Regal Ambassador 233xl Cabin cruiser

description: The first of our 2017 boats are here! Take a look at the actual line of performance Tritoons with up to 300hp, and Chaparral sport boats and wake surf boats with towers! Boating without owning! What a great alternative to boat ownership at a fraction of the cost. The main problem with boating for most busy families is that they don't have the time or the inclination to deal with boat ownership. As a member of the Carefree Boat Club, you have unlimited usage of a new fleet of boats on South Holston, Boone, and Watauga Lakes, as well as nearly 50 other locations across the country. The club boasts a wide variety of pontoon and water sport boats, and we take care of storage, maintenance, cleaning, and insurance. We also offer on the water education and training for our members. You may be a past boat owner or someone who might not consider buying a boat but still wants to experience the freedom and thrill that comes with boating. Schedule a tour today at any of our locations. Feel free to give us a call, email, or visit our website at www.carefreeboats.com/watauga. Boating without the hassle of owning...it's about time!
title: Boating without the hassles of owning! Carefree Boat Club

description: Enjoy the mountain and nautical views from your houseboat or yacht. Experience the cool clear lake waters. The slip is about 17 feet wide and 66 feet long. We recently upgraded to a larger boat slip and now have this one for sale. The slip is located on Watauga Lake in a great marina.  It is nestled in a cove with 15 other houseboat slips and is one of the very few houseboat slips available on Watauga Lake. It is generally protected from the wind and waves. The marina takes care of moving the slip as needed to keep it in deep water year round. The slip has metered electricity for 230v -- 50 amp service and has potable water plumbed to it. Vehicle parking is on a paved roadway near the slip access stairway and ramp. The marina is off of US highway 321 between Elizabethton, TN and Boone, NC.  It is also near Bristol TN so set up your boat to party after the races. If you are renting or planning to rent a houseboat slip, this slip will pay for itself in just a few years through savings in annual slip rental costs. You will own it. Selling price is reduced to $17,460.  Call or text Norm 865-seven40-1429 to view the slip, please leave a message.
title: Yacht slip deep fresh water lake
